Description: The goal of this package is to provide a centralized place to clearly visualize the effects of climate change based on key demographics by country. `mpm` is a package that contains data about various greenhouse gas (GHG) emissions, air pollution metrics in terms of Disability-Adjusted Life Years (DALYs) and internal displacement per country based on GDP and population.
